              <img src="../img/styleguide/listing-controls.png" alt="non-javascript view of pagination layout">
            </p>
            <hr />
            <h3>Component variants</h3>
            <p>The pagination has two significant modes, Numbered pagination and show all infinite scroll. We have illustrated the various states the pagination can display. </p>
